    <item>
      <title>尽管招聘依然强劲，美国失业率仍创两年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/us-payrolls-exceed-expectations-at-275-000-while-wage-gains-cool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管招聘保持健康，美国 2 月份失业率仍攀升至两年高位，表明劳动力市场凉爽但富有弹性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/us-payrolls-exceed-expectations-at-275-000-while-wage-gains-cool</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 13:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
